
<div class="h-[20vh] w-full flex flex-row justify-center items-center bg-slate-100 ">

<form method="post" action="/contact#contact_form" class=" bg-slate-300  w-[60%] grid grid-cols-3  justify-center items-center ">
  <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="customer">
  <input type="hidden" name="utf8" value="✓">
  <input type="email" name="contact[email]" required class="bg-white p-5  col-span-2 outline-none focus:outline-none" placeholder="example@gmail.com">
  <button type="submit" class=" p-5">Subscribe</button>
</form>
</div>



********    Important  Things  ****************


✅ Shopify Contact/Newsletter Form er jonno Required Elements (Point-akare):
<form> tag er modhe action="/contact#contact_form" thakte hobe

Eta Shopify-er built-in route jekhane form data pathay.

method="post" use korte hobe

Shopify form gulo POST method e kaj kore.

<input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="customer"> dite hobe

Eta bolay Shopify ke je eta ekta customer subscription form.

<input type="hidden" name="utf8" value="✓"> thakle bhalo

Shopify compatibility jonno use hoy.

Email input field er name="contact[email]" hote hobe

Shopify email ke identify korte pare.

Email field e required attribute thakle validation hoy

Form submit korle page reload hobe (JavaScript diye prevent korle backend e jabena)

